  "content": "mmit**\n\n```bash\ngit add crates/corvia-kernel/src/lib.rs crates/corvia-kernel/src/chunking_pipeline.rs crates/corvia-cli/src/main.rs crates/corvia-cli/src/workspace.rs\ngit commit -m \"feat(m3.3): wire ChunkingPipeline into CLI ingestion flow (D69)\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 11: E2E Integration Test\n\nVerify the full pipeline end-to-end: source files → chunking pipeline → ProcessedChunks with correct strategy routing, budget enforcement, and metrics.\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `crates/corvia-kernel/src/chunking_pipeline.rs` (add integration test)\n\n**Step 1: Write the E2E test**\n\n```rust\n#[test]\nfn test_e2e_mixed_format_batch() {\n    let config = ChunkingConfig {\n        max_tokens: 100,\n        min_tokens: 5,\n        overlap_tokens: 4,\n        strategy: \"auto\".into(),\n    };\n    let pipeline = ChunkingPipeline::with_kernel_defaults(config);\n\n    let files = vec![\n        SourceFile {\n            content: \"# Title\\n\\nIntro paragraph.\\n\\n## Section\\n\\nContent here.\".into(),\n            metadata: SourceMetadata {\n                file_path: \"README.md\".into(),\n                extension: \"md\".into(),\n                language: Some(\"markdown\".into()),\n                scope_id: \"test\".into(),\n                source_version: \"v1\".into(),\n            },\n        },\n        SourceFile {\n            content: \"[package]\\nname = \\\"test\\\"\\nversion = \\\"0.1.0\\\"\\n\\n[dependencies]\\nserde = \\\"1\\\"\\n\".into(),\n            metadata: SourceMetadata {\n                file_path: \"Cargo.toml\".into(),\n                extension: \"toml\".into(),\n                language: Some(\"toml\".into()),\n                scope_id: \"test\".into(),\n                source_version: \"v1\".into(),\n            },\n        },\n        SourceFile {\n            content: \"Just a plain text file with some content.\".into(),\n            metadata: SourceMetadata {\n                file_path: \"notes.txt\".into(),\n                extension: \"txt\".into(),\n                language: None,\n                scope_id: \"test\".into(),\n                source_version: \"v1\".into(),",
